					<h2>Frequently Asked Questions </h2>				
                What types of systems do you cover under O&amp;M contracts?<p>We cover systems, water pumps, electrical systems, control panels, lighting, plumbing, and more—depending on your project’s requirements.</p>
                Can I customize the O&amp;M contract based on my facility's needs?<p>Yes, all our contracts are customizable in terms of scope, duration, and service frequency.</p>
                Do you provide emergency response services in your contracts?<p>Absolutely. Emergency maintenance and troubleshooting are integral parts of our O&amp;M and technical support contracts.</p>
                How do I track performance under these contracts?<p>We provide detailed monthly reports, KPIs, and real-time monitoring dashboards as part of our service.</p>
                Do you support both government and private sector projects?<p>Yes, we serve public sector institutions, private companies, industrial plants, and infrastructure developers.</p>
